OL,3,CThames Water bosses could have bonuses
OL,4,Cblocked next month
OL,6,FThames Water bosses could see their
OL,7,Fbonuses blocked as soon as next month
OL,8,Funder new powers for Ofwat.
OL,10,FThe Water (Special Measures) Bill gave
OL,11,Fregulator Ofwat powers to ban bonuses
OL,12,Fwhen water companies fail to meet high
OL,13,Fenvironmental standards.
OL,15,FThese will come into force from June,
OL,16,Fmeaning Thames Water's bosses could
OL,17,Fhave their bonuses blocked next month,
OL,18,Fas well as having to return any paid
OL,19,Ffor the last financial year, a
OL,20,FGovernment source said.
