OL,3,CThames Water bosses could have bonuses
OL,4,Cblocked next month
OL,6,FThames Water has been at the centre of
OL,7,Fgrowing public outrage over the extent
OL,8,Fof pollution, rising bills, high
OL,9,Fdividends, and executive pay and
OL,10,Fbonuses at the UK's privatised water
OL,11,Ffirms.
OL,13,FIt also has about #19 billion of debt,
OL,14,Fand was recently allowed to take
OL,15,Fanother high-cost loan which could
OL,16,Freach #3 billion to stave off imminent
OL,17,Fcollapse.
