OL,3,CThames Water bosses could have bonuses
OL,4,Cblocked next month
OL,6,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said:
OL,7,F"Water companies got away with dumping
OL,8,Fa tidal wave of sewage into our rivers
OL,9,Fwhile pocketing millions of pounds of
OL,10,Fbonuses.
OL,12,F"That ends now. The Government will
OL,13,Fban the payment of unfair bonuses for
OL,14,Fpolluting water bosses. The days of
OL,15,Fprofiting from failure are over."
OL,17,FThames Water is England's biggest
OL,18,Fwater firm and supplies about 16
OL,19,Fmillion households across London and
OL,20,Fthe South East.
