OL,3,CThames Water bosses could have bonuses
OL,4,Cblocked next month
OL,6,FIts chairman told MPs this week that
OL,7,Fhundreds of thousands of pounds worth
OL,8,Fof recent bonuses for bosses were
OL,9,Fjustified.
OL,11,F"We live in a competitive marketplace
OL,12,Fand we have to provide the right sort
OL,13,Fof packages to these people otherwise
OL,14,Fthe head hunters come knocking," Sir
OL,15,FAdrian Montague said.
OL,17,FHe admitted that bosses will receive
OL,18,Fmillions of pounds in bonuses as part
OL,19,Fof the #3 billion loan agreed earlier
OL,20,Fthis year.
